snippet.textDisplay:
Mesmerizing indeed. I remember in the first SAARC conference,BTV used this song for the special programs promo. I remember it fondly. In my daughter 's wedding three songs are mandatory. This one ,followed by Shohag Chad and Malka Banur Deshe. I think that I am already dreaming. lol and sigh!This song is a prelude to the tears to come. The daughter leaves the parents home and ahead lies the unknown. How painful is that ! 
Thank you Coke studio team . Regards to all those who are engaged in this endeavor. Thank you.
